Write some code that will read two numbers in from the user and print out the result of dividing them.
It should work like normal division, except that it prints 0 when the denominator is 0, instead of being an error.
To submit your work, and preserve the formatting of your test, create a secret "Gist" atÂ https://gist.github.com/. 
Submit a link to your Gist, as well as any comments or questions you might have.


declare numerador, denominador, resultat

print "introdueix numerador"

read_input numerador

print "introdueix denominador"

read_input denominador

if  denominador = 0 then
  resultat = 0
else 
  resultat = numerador / denominador
end-if

print resultat
